TherOS 2.0.0 requirements

-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=

Apps: File Manager, Installer, Settings (gui frontend for a config)*, manual (so people know what they're doing), program installer (package manager?), Terminal

Environment: Main environment, named lapis (needs: Header text, list of apps, system overview)

Libraries: Library to pull from config, some advanced text library (like text centering, columns, allat), better filesystem lib, 

Extra fun stuff we might want: multitasking, error handling (for file manager, lapis, terminal), maybe some sort of splitscreen interface with tabs?

also something to load the shit on boot, a config file for theme stuffs

* settings app should also have more advanced system info along with therOS version and maybe updates?? (we need a better system for updates lol)

